Package: crtests
Type: Package
Title: Classification and regression tests
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2015-04-28
Authors@R: person("Sjoerd", "van der Spoel", , "R@sjoerdvanderspoel.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides wrapper functions for running classification and regression 
    tests using different machine learning techniques, such as Random Forests 
    and decision trees. The package provides standardized methods for preparing 
    data to suit the algorithm's needs, training a model, making predictions, and 
    evaluating results. Also, some functions are provided to run multiple 
    instances of a test.
